# infrastructure/docker/Dockerfile.agents
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PURPOSE:
#     Docker image for the agent worker process.
#     Runs the Kafka consumer loop that triggers all agent pipelines.
#
# WHAT GOES HERE:
#     Base image: python:3.11-slim
#     Additional system deps: libgomp1 (for scikit-learn/PyTorch),
#                             libgl1-mesa-glx (for PaddleOCR image processing)
#     Install all Python dependencies via poetry
#     Download ML model on build (LayoutLMv3 from Hugging Face)
#     Copy source code
#     CMD: python -m orchestration.orchestrator_agent
#          (starts the Kafka consumer event loop)
#
#     MODEL CACHING:
#         LayoutLMv3 and BAAI/bge-large models downloaded at build time
#         and cached in the image layer. This avoids download delays
#         at runtime and makes model version explicit in the image tag.
#
#     RESOURCE REQUIREMENTS:
#         Memory: 4GB minimum (ML models in memory)
#         CPU: 2 cores minimum
#         GPU: optional — if CUDA available, PaddleOCR uses GPU automatically
#
#     HEALTHCHECK:
#         Check that the Kafka consumer is running and connected.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
